WEBVTT

00:02.168 --> 00:03.919
ANNOUNCER:
Previously on The Vampire Diaries:

00:04.129 --> 00:06.296
- You took everything.
- Let bygones be bygones.

00:06.506 --> 00:09.049
- Resentment gets old.
STEFAN: Know what never gets old?

00:09.259 --> 00:10.300
- Revenge.
- No.

00:10.510 --> 00:11.969
What, Klaus? Missing something?

00:12.178 --> 00:13.387
Three sleeping Originals.

00:13.596 --> 00:16.097
Four coffins.
Who is in the lockbox?

00:16.306 --> 00:19.518
He's been sired. He feels loyal to Klaus.
Klaus' blood created him.

00:19.728 --> 00:22.354
He released me from a curse
that was ruining my life.

00:22.564 --> 00:24.898
- I owe him for that.
- Bite your girlfriend.

00:25.108 --> 00:26.900
A hybrid bite would kill a vampire.

00:27.110 --> 00:29.903
Consider this me putting
your undying loyalty to the test.

00:30.113 --> 00:32.613
Klaus can't control me,
not when it comes to you.

00:32.824 --> 00:34.074
Ugh. Ouch!

00:34.284 --> 00:36.452
- Oh, no.
- Did you just bite me?

00:36.703 --> 00:38.120
- Caroline.
- Get away from me!

